I am in the same boat too. My duo partner for 8 months became my best friend last October, than my boyfriend last Christmas.

The thing that depresses me though is that I might lose him. He hates LoL now because he believes now that he will never get back to platinum and will just demote himself to Bronze. I love him, but League is literally my life. I have no other hobbies. I tried other videogames but got bored quick. Tried WoW with my bf, which is what he purely plays now, but I am already bored of it. League is what bound us, but now it might tear us apart. 

;_;

Congratsu!

Just got my girlfriend into leagues so I hope we endure the same lovely destiny as you two!

